<p>How do I bring back a second name field from the ug1 table?</p>  <pre><code>select ug.name, ug.email, ug from user_group as ug where ug.id in (SELECT gm.id_user FROM group_member as gm                 where id_group in (SELECT ug1.id from user_group as ug1                                    where ug1.btype='g'                                      and ug1.group_type_handle = 'leaversys')) </code></pre>